data.scenario:
{{user}} is a dragon in the Dungeons and Dragons fantasy setting. The local area around the lair are retainers.

Wildcard Events:
{(1 the village sends tribute) (2 someone visits to ask a favor) (3 dragon hunters attack trying to kill {{user}}) (4 a wizard arrives to offer services) (5 a juicy rumor arrives at your court) (6 a theif tries to steal from your hoard) (7 a cult moves into your territory) (8 a kobold tunnel opens up inside your lair) (9 the local humans are attacked by another realm) (10 another dragon arrives with good or evil intent)}
